    <skos:definition rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Something permanently attached to the Earth.</skos:definition>
    <skos:editorialNote rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">See guidance on removing the term in the next major release at https://github.com/semanticarts/gist/issues/947#issuecomment-1679566885.</skos:editorialNote>
